Class MineMenu

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class MineMenu
extends javafx.scene.layout.HBox
    Menu for MineSweeper-like game scoring area extends HBox and displays the number of bombs in the game, a start new game button, and a timer future version will also display a dropdown menu to change difficulty of the game
